<HL>
   Technology:
   U.S. Takes Up Inquiry
   Into Microchip's Invention
</HL>
<DATE>
04/03/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B8
</SO>
<CO>
   SCE TXN
</CO>
